title: ‘Euphoria’ Season 2, Episode 2 Recap
description:
Joanna and Nora rejoin to discuss the delightful teen romp that is 'Euphoria' Season 2, Episode 2. They discuss the fascinating montage involving Cassy and Nate (13:42). they also discuss the newly introduced character this season and much more!
Hosts: Joanna Robinson and Nora Princiotti
Producer: Steve Ahlman
